LOUIS' AND ( flight_1.meal_code = food_service_1.meal_code AND food_service_1.meal_description = 'DINNER' AND ( ( flight_1.flight_days = days_1.days_code AND days_1.day_name = date_day_1.day_name AND date_day_1.year = 1991 AND date_day_1.month_number = 5 AND date_day_1.day_number = 6 AND ( flight_1.departure_time >= 1800 AND flight_1.departure_time <= 2359 ) ) OR ( flight_1.flight_days = days_1.days_code AND days_1.day_name = date_day_1.day_name AND date_day_1.year = 1991 AND date_day_1.month_number = 5 AND date_day_1.day_number = 7 AND ( flight_1.departure_time >= 0 AND flight_1.departure_time <= 600 ) ) ) ) ) )

PAUL' AND ( flight_1.to_airport = airport_service_2.airport_code AND airport_service_2.city_code = city_2.city_code AND city_2.city_name = 'KANSAS CITY' AND ( flight_1.flight_days = days_1.days_code AND days_1.day_name = date_day_1.day_name AND date_day_1.year = 1991 AND date_day_1.month_number = 6 AND date_day_1.day_number = 25 AND flight_1.meal_code = food_service_1.meal_code AND food_service_1.meal_description = 'BREAKFAST' ) )

what is the lowest price fare from atlanta to san francisco on flight delta 82 and delta 139 ||| SELECT DISTINCT fare_1.fare_id FROM fare fare_1 , flight_fare flight_fare_1 , flight flight_1 , airport_service airport_service_1 , city city_1 , airport_service airport_service_2 , city city_2 , flight_leg flight_leg_1 , flight flight_2 WHERE fare_1.one_direction_cost = ( SELECT MIN ( fare_1.one_direction_cost ) FROM fare fare_1 , flight_fare flight_fare_1 , flight flight_1 , airport_service airport_service_1 , city city_1 , airport_service airport_service_2 , city city_2 , flight_leg flight_leg_1 , flight flight_2 WHERE fare_1.fare_id = flight_fare_1.fare_id AND flight_fare_1.flight_id = flight_1.flight_id AND flight_1.from_airport = airport_service_1.airport_code AND airport_service_1.city_code = city_1.city_code AND city_1.city_name = 'ATLANTA' AND ( flight_1.to_airport = airport_service_2.airport_code AND airport_service_2.city_code = city_2.city_code AND city_2.city_name = 'SAN FRANCISCO' AND flight_1.flight_id = flight_leg_1.flight_id AND flight_leg_1.leg_flight = flight_2.flight_id AND flight_2.airline_code = 'DL' AND ( flight_2.flight_number = 82 OR flight_2.flight_number = 139 ) ) ) AND fare_1.fare_id = flight_fare_1.fare_id AND flight_fare_1.flight_id = flight_1.flight_id AND flight_1.from_airport = airport_service_1.airport_code AND airport_service_1.city_code = city_1.city_code AND city_1.city_name = 'ATLANTA' AND ( flight_1.to_airport = airport_service_2.airport_code AND airport_service_2.city_code = city_2.city_code AND city_2.city_name = 'SAN FRANCISCO' AND flight_1.flight_id = flight_leg_1.flight_id AND flight_leg_1.leg_flight = flight_2.flight_id AND flight_2.airline_code = 'DL' AND ( flight_2.flight_number = 82 OR flight_2.flight_number = 139 ) )

list the nonstop flights from miami to new york on a sunday along with the fares that are less than 466 dollars ||| SELECT DISTINCT flight_1.flight_id FROM flight flight_1 , flight_fare flight_fare_1 , fare fare_1 , airport_service airport_service_1 , city city_1 , airport_service airport_service_2 , city city_2 , days days_1 , fare_basis fare_basis_1 , days days_2 WHERE flight_1.stops = 0 AND ( flight_1.from_airport = airport_service_1.airport_code AND airport_service_1.city_code = city_1.city_code AND city_1.city_name = 'MIAMI' AND ( flight_1.to_airport = airport_service_2.airport_code AND airport_service_2.city_code = city_2.city_code AND city_2.city_name = 'NEW YORK' AND flight_1.flight_days = days_1.days_code AND days_1.day_name = 'SUNDAY' ) ) AND flight_1.flight_id = flight_fare_1.flight_id AND flight_fare_1.fare_id = fare_1.fare_id AND ( fare_1.one_direction_cost < 466 AND fare_1.fare_basis_code = fare_basis_1.fare_basis_code AND fare_basis_1.basis_days = days_2.days_code AND days_2.day_name = 'SUNDAY' )

how many fares are there one way from tacoma to montreal ||| SELECT count ( DISTINCT fare_1.fare_id ) FROM fare fare_1 , flight_fare flight_fare_1 , flight flight_1 , airport_service airport_service_1 , city city_1 , airport_service airport_service_2 , city city_2 WHERE fare_1.round_trip_required = 'NO' AND fare_1.fare_id = flight_fare_1.fare_id AND flight_fare_1.flight_id = flight_1.flight_id AND flight_1.from_airport = airport_service_1.airport_code AND airport_service_1.city_code = city_1.city_code AND city_1.city_name = 'TACOMA' AND flight_1.to_airport = airport_service_2.airport_code AND airport_service_2.city_code = city_2.city_code AND city_2.city_name = 'MONTREAL'

how many daily us air flights are there between philadelphia and pittsburgh ||| SELECT count ( DISTINCT flight_1.flight_id ) FROM flight flight_1 , airport_service airport_service_1 , city city_1 , airport_service airport_service_2 , city city_2 WHERE flight_1.flight_days = 'DAILY' AND ( flight_1.airline_code = 'US' AND ( flight_1.from_airport = airport_service_1.airport_code AND airport_service_1.city_code = city_1.city_code AND city_1.city_name = 'PHILADELPHIA' AND flight_1.to_airport = airport_service_2.airport_code AND airport_service_2.city_code = city_2.city_code AND city_2.city_name = 'PITTSBURGH' ) )
what does ewr mean ||| SELECT DISTINCT airport_1.airport_code FROM airport airport_1 WHERE airport_1.airport_code = 'EWR'
is there a late afternoon flight leaving washington for denver ||| SELECT DISTINCT flight_1.flight_id FROM flight flight_1 , airport_service airport_service_1 , city city_1 , airport_service airport_service_2 , city city_2 WHERE flight_1.departure_time BETWEEN 1600 AND 1800 AND ( flight_1.from_airport = airport_service_1.airport_code AND airport_service_1.city_code = city_1.city_code AND city_1.city_name = 'WASHINGTON' AND flight_1.to_airport = airport_service_2.airport_code AND airport_service_2.city_code = city_2.city_code AND city_2.city_name = 'DENVER' )

how expensive is the san francisco limousine service ||| SELECT DISTINCT ground_service_1.ground_fare FROM ground_service ground_service_1 , city city_1 WHERE ground_service_1.transport_type = 'LIMOUSINE' AND ground_service_1.city_code = city_1.city_code AND city_1.city_name = 'SAN FRANCISCO'

find me the flights that are nonstop between boston and dallas that leave between 12 and 2 in the afternoon ||| SELECT DISTINCT flight_1.flight_id FROM flight flight_1 , airport_service airport_service_1 , city city_1 , airport_service airport_service_2 , city city_2 WHERE flight_1.stops = 0 AND ( flight_1.from_airport = airport_service_1.airport_code AND airport_service_1.city_code = city_1.city_code AND city_1.city_name = 'BOSTON' AND ( flight_1.to_airport = airport_service_2.airport_code AND airport_service_2.city_code = city_2.city_code AND city_2.city_name = 'DALLAS' AND ( flight_1.departure_time >= 1200 AND flight_1.departure_time <= 1400 ) ) )

PETERSBURG' AND ( flight_1.to_airport = airport_service_2.airport_code AND airport_service_2.city_code = city_2.city_code AND city_2.city_name = 'TORONTO' AND flight_1.flight_id = flight_fare_1.flight_id AND flight_fare_1.fare_id = fare_1.fare_id AND fare_1.round_trip_cost IS NOT NULL )

show me the flights from atlanta to washington dc on wednesday night and thursday morning ||| SELECT DISTINCT flight_1.flight_id FROM flight flight_1 , airport_service airport_service_1 , city city_1 , airport_service airport_service_2 , city city_2 , days days_1 , date_day date_day_1 WHERE flight_1.from_airport = airport_service_1.airport_code AND airport_service_1.city_code = city_1.city_code AND city_1.city_name = 'ATLANTA' AND ( flight_1.to_airport = airport_service_2.airport_code AND airport_service_2.city_code = city_2.city_code AND city_2.city_name = 'WASHINGTON' AND ( ( flight_1.flight_days = days_1.days_code AND days_1.day_name = date_day_1.day_name AND date_day_1.year = 1991 AND date_day_1.month_number = 4 AND date_day_1.day_number = 23 AND ( ( flight_1.departure_time NOT BETWEEN 601 AND 1759 ) AND ( flight_1.departure_time >= 1800 AND flight_1.departure_time <= 2400 ) ) ) OR ( flight_1.flight_days = days_1.days_code AND days_1.day_name = date_day_1.day_name AND date_day_1.year = 1991 AND date_day_1.month_number = 4 AND date_day_1.day_number = 23 AND ( flight_1.departure_time BETWEEN 0 AND 1200 ) ) ) )

how many flights come from denver to baltimore on july nineteenth ||| SELECT count ( DISTINCT flight_1.flight_id ) FROM flight flight_1 , airport_service airport_service_1 , city city_1 , airport_service airport_service_2 , city city_2 , days days_1 , date_day date_day_1 WHERE ( flight_1.from_airport = airport_service_1.airport_code AND airport_service_1.city_code = city_1.city_code AND city_1.city_name = 'DENVER' AND flight_1.to_airport = airport_service_2.airport_code AND airport_service_2.city_code = city_2.city_code AND city_2.city_name = 'BALTIMORE' ) AND ( ( flight_1.flight_days = days_1.days_code AND days_1.day_name = date_day_1.day_name AND date_day_1.year = 1991 AND date_day_1.month_number = 7 AND date_day_1.day_number = 19 AND not ( ( flight_1.arrival_time < flight_1.departure_time ) ) ) OR ( flight_1.flight_days = days_1.days_code AND days_1.day_name = date_day_1.day_name AND date_day_1.year = 1991 AND date_day_1.month_number = 7 AND date_day_1.day_number = 18 AND ( flight_1.arrival_time < flight_1.departure_time ) ) )

city_1.city_name = 'PHILADELPHIA' AND ( flight_1.to_airport = airport_service_2.airport_code AND airport_service_2.city_code = city_2.city_code AND city_2.city_name = 'SAN FRANCISCO' AND ( flight_leg_1.flight_id AND flight_leg_1.leg_flight = flight_2.flight_id AND flight_2.from_airport = airport_service_4.airport_code AND airport_service_4.city_code = city_4.city_code AND city_4.city_name = 'PHILADELPHIA' AND ( flight_2.to_airport = airport_service_5.airport_code AND airport_service_5.city_code = city_5.city_code AND city_5.city_name = 'DALLAS' AND ( flight_1.flight_days = days_2.days_code AND days_2.day_name = date_day_2.day_name AND date_day_2.year = 1991 AND date_day_2.month_number = 5 AND date_day_2.day_number = 24 AND ( not ( ( what flights can i take between boston and atlanta so that when i leave boston i will have the maximum amount of time on the ground in atlanta and still return in the same day ||| SELECT DISTINCT flight_1.flight_id FROM flight flight_1 , airport_service airport_service_1 , city city_1 , airport_service airport_service_2 , city city_2 WHERE ( flight_1.from_airport = airport_service_1.airport_code AND airport_service_1.city_code = city_1.city_code AND city_1.city_name = 'BOSTON' AND ( flight_1.to_airport = airport_service_2.airport_code AND airport_service_2.city_code = city_2.city_code AND city_2.city_name = 'ATLANTA' AND flight_1.arrival_time = ( SELECT MIN ( arrival_time ) FROM flight flight_1 , airport_service airport_service_1 , city city_1 , airport_service airport_service_2 , city city_2 WHERE flight_1.from_airport = airport_service_1.airport_code AND airport_service_1.city_code = city_1.city_code AND city_1.city_name = 'BOSTON' AND flight_1.to_airport = airport_service_2.airport_code AND airport_service_2.city_code = city_2.city_code AND city_2.city_name = 'ATLANTA' ) ) ) OR ( flight_1.from_airport = airport_service_1.airport_code AND airport_service_1.city_code = city_1.city_code AND city_1.city_name = 'ATLANTA' AND ( flight_1.to_airport = airport_service_2.airport_code AND airport_service_2.city_code = city_2.city_code AND city_2.city_name = 'BOSTON' AND flight_1.departure_time = ( SELECT MAX ( departure_time ) FROM flight flight_1 , airport_service airport_service_1 , city city_1 , airport_service airport_service_2 , city city_2 WHERE flight_1.from_airport = airport_service_1.airport_code AND airport_service_1.city_code = city_1.city_code AND city_1.city_name = 'ATLANTA' AND ( flight_1.to_airport = airport_service_2.airport_code AND airport_service_2.city_code = city_2.city_code AND city_2.city_name = 'BOSTON' AND not ( ( flight_1.arrival_time < flight_1.departure_time ) ) ) ) ) )

show me the flight from detroit to westchester county with the highest one way fare ||| SELECT DISTINCT flight_1.flight_id FROM flight flight_1 , flight_fare flight_fare_1 , fare fare_1 , airport_service airport_service_1 , city city_1 , airport_service airport_service_2 , city city_2 WHERE flight_1.flight_id = flight_fare_1.flight_id AND flight_fare_1.fare_id = fare_1.fare_id AND fare_1.one_direction_cost = ( SELECT MAX ( fare_1.one_direction_cost ) FROM fare fare_1 , flight_fare flight_fare_1 , flight flight_1 , airport_service airport_service_1 , city city_1 , airport_service airport_service_2 , city city_2 WHERE fare_1.round_trip_required = 'NO' AND fare_1.fare_id = flight_fare_1.fare_id AND flight_fare_1.flight_id = flight_1.flight_id AND flight_1.from_airport = airport_service_1.airport_code AND airport_service_1.city_code = city_1.city_code AND city_1.city_name = 'DETROIT' AND flight_1.to_airport = airport_service_2.airport_code AND airport_service_2.city_code = city_2.city_code AND city_2.city_name = 'WESTCHESTER COUNTY' ) AND fare_1.round_trip_required = 'NO' AND ( flight_1.from_airport = airport_service_1.airport_code AND airport_service_1.city_code = city_1.city_code AND city_1.city_name = 'DETROIT' AND flight_1.to_airport = airport_service_2.airport_code AND airport_service_2.city_code = city_2.city_code AND city_2.city_name = 'WESTCHESTER COUNTY' )

what flights depart baltimore and arrive by 8pm friday in san francisco ||| SELECT DISTINCT flight_1.flight_id FROM flight flight_1 , airport_service airport_service_1 , city city_1 , airport_service airport_service_2 , city city_2 , days days_1 , date_day date_day_1 WHERE flight_1.from_airport = airport_service_1.airport_code AND airport_service_1.city_code = city_1.city_code AND city_1.city_name = 'BALTIMORE' AND ( flight_1.to_airport = airport_service_2.airport_code AND airport_service_2.city_code = city_2.city_code AND city_2.city_name = 'SAN FRANCISCO' AND ( ( flight_1.flight_days = days_1.days_code AND days_1.day_name = date_day_1.day_name AND date_day_1.year = 1991 AND date_day_1.month_number = 6 AND date_day_1.day_number = 25 AND ( ( flight_1.departure_time > flight_1.arrival_time AND ( flight_1.time_elapsed >= 60 OR flight_1.arrival_time < 41 ) ) AND flight_1.arrival_time < 2000 ) ) OR ( flight_1.flight_days = days_1.days_code AND days_1.day_name = date_day_1.day_name AND date_day_1.year = 1991 AND date_day_1.month_number = 6 AND date_day_1.day_number = 25 AND ( not ( ( flight_1.departure_time > flight_1.arrival_time AND ( flight_1.time_elapsed >= 60 OR flight_1.arrival_time < 41 ) ) ) AND flight_1.arrival_time < 2000 ) ) ) )
